data.description: Introducing this versatile 3-bed, 1-bath home with commercial zoning! Enjoy spacious bedrooms, one with a flexible sitting area. NEWER ROOF (2020) & A/C (2022)! Recently renovated bathroom adds luxury. Outside, a large backyard hosts an above-ground pool. Two-car garage offers ample storage. Conveniently located near amenities and transport. Explore the endless possibilities this property offers today!
